 <li><a href="http://aleph0.clarku.edu/~djoyce/java/elements/elements.html" target="other">Dynamic version of Euclid&rsquo;s Elements</a>,
 by D.E. Joyce, Clark University.</li>
 <li><a href="https://www.geogebra.org/m/m3QuM3Kn" target="other">Projective geometry in Geogebra</a></li>
 <li><a href="https://www.cs.unm.edu/~joel/NonEuclid/" target="other">NonEuclid: Interactive Javascript Software for Creating Straightedge and Collapsible Compass Constructions in the Poincar&eacute; Disk Model of Hyperbolic Geometry</a>,
 by Joel Castellanos, Joe Dan Austin, Ervan Darnell.</li>
</ul>
